com.b2international.snowowl.snomed.datastore.id.reservations

Interface ISnomedIdentiferReservationService


  • public interface ISnomedIdentiferReservationService
    SNOMED CT Identifier reservation service interface. Capable of creating reservation of SNOMED CT Identifiers. A Reservation is denoted by a simple unique name.
    Since:
    4.0

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      void create(java.lang.String reservationName, Reservation reservation)
      Create a SNOMED CT Identifier Reservation in the system to restrict certain identifiers from being generated for new components.
      void delete(java.lang.String reservationName)
      Delete a previously created reservation.
      Reservation getReservation(java.lang.String reservationName)
      Returns a Reservation item found by the defined reservationName.
      java.util.Collection<Reservation> getReservations()
      Returns all current Reservation in the system.
      boolean isReserved(java.lang.String componentId)
      Returns whether the given componentId is reserved for later use or not.
